  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Schweizerhof is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner taken in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of an excellent range of hot and cold buffet food.</p>
<p>Dinner includes a four course evening meal with a choice of menu.</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinner is included.</p>
<p>Free daily afternoon buffet with cold meats, cheese and select of cakes available.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>Guests return year after year to this attractive hotel, which is deservedly a favourite in our programme. The facilities at the Schweizerhof are amongst the best in <a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee</a> and high standards of service and cuisine are assured.</p>
<h2>Nature lovers</h2>
<p>The hotel is situated amid the pristine scenery of the Swiss Alps and is a fantastic choice if you're hoping to connect with nature during your ski holiday. Hotel Schweizerhof aim to make you feel every bit as relaxed as you would be in your own home whilst giving you a genuine Alpine experience. </p>
<h2>Restaurant Hofsaal</h2>
<p>The hotels kitchen is known for its excellent cuisine. You'll find all the dishes are made from fresh Swiss ingredients as well as specially picked ingredients from all over the world. You can enjoy a 4 course menu for dinner with a choice of menu, but no matter your choice, each dish is crafted with care and respect. </p>
<h2>Swiss bliss</h2>
<p>Your stay at Hotel Schweizerhof will include access to some fantastic spa facilities. The spa offers an indoor swimming pool, whirlpool, multiple different saunas, steam baths and infrared cabins. If you'd like a massage or beauty treatment, the hotels expert therapists will be happy to help you indulge in their treatments which are specially designed to soothe the mind and body - perfect for after ski relaxation. </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
