  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is located a one minute walk (100 metres) from the centre of the village, and the ski bus stop.</p>
<p>It is Approx. seven minutes' walk (700 metres) to the ski lifts.</p>
<p>There is a free hotel shuttle bus service to the lifts on request (Sunday-Friday, approx. 9-11.30am and 2-5pm).</p>
<p> </p>]]></locationDescription>
