  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Winter Garden twin rooms</strong> are around 26m² and have a bath or shower. These rooms are north facing.</p>
<p><strong>Standard twin rooms</strong> are around 34m² and have a bath. These rooms are west facing and have a balcony and can sleep a third guest on an additional bed.</p>
<p><strong>Superior twin rooms</strong> are around 38m² and have a bath. These rooms are south facing and have a balcony and can also sleep up to three.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe twin rooms</strong> are similar to Superior rooms but they are around 42m² and have a shower. These rooms are on request so please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>are around 22m² and have a shower and north facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Cable/satellite TV</li>
<li>Hair dryer </li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
